<!--分類-->
伊波拉病毒屬的成員為已有數百萬年歷史的[[絲狀病毒科|絲狀病毒]]之一。<ref name="Cite pmid| 20569424">{{cite journal |author = Taylor DJ, Leach RW, Bruenn J | title = Filoviruses are ancient and integrated into mammalian genomes | journal = BMC Evolutionary Biology | volume = 10 | pages = 193 | year = 2010 | pmid = 20569424 | pmc = 2906475 | doi = 10.1186/1471-2148-10-193 }}</ref>病毒學家利用{{link-en|分子時鐘法|Molecular clock}}追溯當中的源流，發現伊波拉與馬爾堡病毒雖極為相似，但其實早已於數千年前分化。<ref>{{cite journal |author = Suzuki Y, Gojobori T | title = The origin and evolution of Ebola and Marburg viruses |url = https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-biology-and-evolution_1997-08_14_8/page/800 | journal = Molecular Biology and Evolution | volume = 14 | issue = 8 | pages = 800–6 | year = 1997 | pmid = 9254917 | doi=10.1093/oxfordjournals.molbev.a025820}}</ref>

<!--形態-->
與其他絲狀病毒一樣，伊波拉病毒體型修長。它們呈“6”或“U”字狀，有時亦會捲曲成環狀，並帶分支。這類病毒的平均寬度為80[[納米|納米]]，長度參差甚大——從974到14,000納米不等。<ref name=Geisbert1995>{{cite journal |author = Geisbert TW, Jahrling PB | title = Differentiation of filoviruses by electron microscopy | journal = Virus research | volume = 39 | issue = 2–3 | pages = 129–150 | year = 1995 | pmid = 8837880 | doi=10.1016/0168-1702(95)00080-1}}</ref>

<!--基因-->
伊波拉病毒具有線性、非結段型、不具感染性的單鏈[[基因組|核糖核酸基因組]]。此基因組帶負極性，並具有逆互補性的3'及5'極端。其不含[[5'端帽|5'端帽]]、不具[[多腺苷酸化|多腺苷酸化]]性，亦並非以共價鍵與[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]相連。<ref name=Fauquet2005>{{Cite book |last1 = Pringle | first1 = C. R. | chapter = Order Mononegavirales | year = 2005 | editor-last = Fauquet | editor-first = C. M. | editor2-last = Mayo | editor2-first = M. A. | editor3-last = Maniloff | editor3-first = J. | editor4-last = Desselberger | editor4-first = U. | editor5-last = Ball | editor5-first = L. A. | title = Virus Taxonomy – Eighth Report of the International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses | pages = 609–614 | publisher = Elsevier/Academic Press | location = San Diego, US | isbn = 0-12-370200-3 | ref = harv}}</ref>它們的基因組約有[[鹼基對|一千個鹼基對]]，內含7個以“{{lang|en|3'-UTR-NP-VP35-VP40-GP-VP30-VP24-L-5'-UTR}}”次序排列的[[基因|基因]]。<ref name = Kiley1982>{{cite journal |author = Kiley MP, Bowen ET, Eddy GA, Isaäcson M, Johnson KM, McCormick JB, Murphy FA, Pattyn SR, Peters D, Prozesky OW, Regnery RL, Simpson DI, Slenczka W, Sureau P, van der Groen G, Webb PA, Wulff H | title = Filoviridae: A taxonomic home for Marburg and Ebola viruses? | journal = Intervirology | volume = 18 | issue = 1–2 | pages = 24–32 | year = 1982 | pmid = 7118520 | doi = 10.1159/000149300 }}</ref>這五種伊波拉病毒的基因組以基因重疊的位置及數量區分。

<!--遺傳-->
伊波拉病毒會與宿主體內特定的細胞[[受體_(生物化學)|受體]]（如：“{{link-en|DC-SIGN|DC-SIGN}}”、[[C-型凝集素|C-型凝集素]]及[[整合素|整合素]]）結合進行[[胞飲作用|胞飲作用]]，開始它們的[[生物生命週期|生命週期]]。<ref name="Misasi2014">{{cite journal|author=Misasi J, Sullivan NJ|title=Camouflage and Misdirection: The Full-On Assault of Ebola Virus Disease|journal=Cell|volume=159|issue=3|pages=477–86|date=October 2014|pmid=25417101|doi=10.1016/j.cell.2014.10.006}}</ref>成功入侵後，病毒會移動至[[細胞|細胞]]的[[核內體|核內體]]和[[溶酶體|溶酶體]]處，使自身含有獨特[[糖蛋白|糖蛋白]]（“{{lang|en|GP1}}”及“{{lang|en|GP2}}”）的包膜分解，以便和[[細胞膜|細胞膜]]內壁的蛋白物融合並釋放病毒核衣殼。<ref name="Misasi2014"/><ref name="Kuhl2012">{{cite journal|author=Kühl A, Pöhlmann S|title=How Ebola virus counters the interferon system|journal=Zoonoses Public Health|volume=59|issue=Supplement 2|pages=116–31|date=September 2012|pmid=22958256|doi=10.1111/j.1863-2378.2012.01454.x}}</ref>由 ''L'' [[基因|基因]]編碼的病毒[[核糖核酸聚合酶|核糖核酸聚合酶]]解封核衣殼，並將有關基因[[轉錄|轉錄]]為正荷單鏈[[信使核糖核酸|信使核糖核酸]]。此核糖核酸後進一步被翻譯為數種結構與非結構性蛋白物，其中以核蛋白的數量最多，它的濃度亦決定著何時從基因轉錄推進至基因組複製。基因組複製會產生完整的抗基因組物質，並被再轉錄為新病毒的基因組。<ref name="Olejnik2011">{{cite journal | author = Olejnik J, Ryabchikova E, Corley RB, Mühlberger E | title = Intracellular events and cell fate in filovirus infection | journal = Viruses | volume = 3 | issue = 8 | pages = 1501–31 | date = 08-2011 | pmid = 21927676 | pmc = 3172725 | doi = 10.3390/v3081501 }}</ref>此乃伊波拉病毒自我複製的方式。新產生的病毒組合物，會聚集到細胞膜的內壁將之穿破，沿途亦會奪取適用的合成物以製造自身的包膜。新生病毒繼續襲擊其他細胞，並重複以上週期。伊波拉病毒的[[病毒性|特質]]使研究工作困難重重。<ref name=Feldmann2005>{{Cite book | last1 = Feldmann | first1 = H. | last2 = Geisbert | first2 = T. W. | last3 = Jahrling | first3 = P. B. | last4 = Klenk | first4 = H.-D. | last5 = Netesov | first5 = S. V. | last6 = Peters | first6 = C. J. | last7 = Sanchez | first7 = A. | last8 = Swanepoel | first8 = R. | last9 = Volchkov | first9 = V. E. | chapter = Family Filoviridae | year = 2005 | editor-last = Fauquet | editor-first = C. M. | editor2-last = Mayo | editor2-first = M. A. | editor3-last = Maniloff | editor3-first = J. | editor4-last = Desselberger | editor4-first = U. | editor5-last = Ball | editor5-first = L. A. | title = Virus Taxonomy – Eighth Report of the International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses | pages = 645–653 | publisher = Elsevier/Academic Press | location = San Diego, US | isbn = 0-12-370200-3 }}</ref>

===天然宿主===
目前還未能鐵定伊波拉病毒的[[天然宿主|天然宿主]]，但是根據過往的調查，[[蝙蝠|蝙蝠]]（尤其是[[錘頭果蝠|錘頭果蝠]]、{{link-en|反曲肩果蝠|Franquet's epauletted fruit bat}}及{{link-en|小領果蝠|Little collared fruit bat}}）的機會最高。<ref name="Chowell2014"/><ref>{{cite journal|author=Laupland KB, Valiquette L|title=Ebola virus disease|journal=Can J Infect Dis Med Microbiol|volume=25|issue=3|pages=128–9|date=05-2014|pmid=25285105|pmc=4173971|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4173971/|accessdate=2015-02-21|archive-date=2022-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220203202137/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4173971/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1996年發表的一份報告指出，在24種植物及19種[[脊椎動物|脊椎動物]]中，只有蝙蝠受到伊波拉病毒（模式種）的感染，可它們事後並沒有發病，此乃天然宿主的一大特點。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Swanepoel R, Leman PA, Burt FJ, Zachariades NA, Braack LE, Ksiazek TG, Rollin PE, Zaki SR, Peters CJ | title = Experimental inoculation of plants and animals with Ebola virus | journal = Emerging Infectious Diseases | volume = 2 | issue = 4 | pages = 321–325 | date = Oct 1996 | pmid = 8969248 | pmc = 2639914 | doi = 10.3201/eid0204.960407 | issn = 1080-6040 | url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2639914/ | accessdate = 2015-02-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211101123458/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2639914/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>1976-98年期間，共有30,000隻哺乳類、鳥類、爬行類、兩棲類及節肢類動物接受檢驗，惟研究者只在六隻[[中非共和國|中非共和國]]的[[囓齒動物|囓齒動物]]（{{link-en|彼得鼠|Peters's mouse}}與[[非洲柔毛鼠屬|非洲柔毛鼠]]）及一隻[[鼩鼱科|鼩鼱動物]]（{{link-en|大森林鼩鼱|Greater forest shrew}}）的體內找到過病毒的遺傳痕跡，其他均一無所獲。<ref name="Pourrut2005">{{cite journal |author = Pourrut X, Kumulungui B, Wittmann T, Moussavou G, Délicat A, Yaba P, Nkoghe D, Gonzalez JP, Leroy EM | title = The natural history of Ebola virus in Africa | journal = Microbes and infection / Institut Pasteur | volume = 7 | issue = 7–8 | pages = 1005–1014 | year = 2005 | pmid = 16002313 | doi = 10.1016/j.micinf.2005.04.006 }}</ref><ref name="Morvan1999">{{cite journal |author = Morvan JM, Deubel V, Gounon P, Nakouné E, Barrière P, Murri S, Perpète O, Selekon B, Coudrier D, Gautier-Hion A, Colyn M, Volehkov V | title = Identification of Ebola virus sequences present as RNA or DNA in organs of terrestrial small mammals of the Central African Republic | journal = Microbes and Infection | volume = 1 | issue = 14 | pages = 1193–1201 | year = 1999 | pmid = 10580275 | doi = 10.1016/S1286-4579(99)00242-7 }}</ref>2001及2003年疾病爆發期間，人們在一些大猩猩及黑猩猩的屍體中，發現伊波拉病毒（模式種）的構成物。可此病對靈長動物的殺傷力高，故他們作為天然宿主的機會微乎其微。<ref name="Pourrut2005" /><ref name="Groseth2007">{{cite journal|author=Groseth A, Feldmann H, Strong JE|title=The ecology of Ebola virus|journal=Trends Microbiol|volume=15|issue=9|pages=408–16|date=09-2007|pmid=17698361|doi=10.1016/j.tim.2007.08.001}}</ref>一項於2002-03年、涉及1,030隻動物的實驗顯示，679隻[[加蓬|加蓬]]及[[剛果|剛果]]蝙蝠中的13隻，帶有模式種的[[核糖核酸|核糖核酸]]片段。<ref>{{cite journal |author = Leroy EM, Kumulungui B, Pourrut X, Rouquet P, Hassanin A, Yaba P, Délicat A, Paweska JT, Gonzalez JP, Swanepoel R | title = Fruit bats as reservoirs of Ebola virus | journal = Nature | volume = 438 | issue = 7068 | pages = 575–576 | year = 2005 | pmid = 16319873 | doi = 10.1038/438575a | bibcode = 2005Natur.438..575L }}</ref>專家另也於[[孟加拉國|孟加拉國]]的果蝠身上，找到針對模式種及雷斯頓種的[[抗體|抗體]]，故伊波拉病原體亦可能存在於[[亞洲|亞洲]]。<ref name="pmid23343532">{{cite journal |author = Olival KJ, Islam A, Yu M, Anthony SJ, Epstein JH, Khan SA, Khan SU, Crameri G, Wang LF, Lipkin WI, Luby SP, Daszak P | title = Ebola virus antibodies in fruit bats, bangladesh | journal = Emerging Infect. Dis. | volume = 19 | issue = 2 | pages = 270–3 | year = 2013 | pmid = 23343532 | pmc = 3559038 | doi = 10.3201/eid1902.120524 }}</ref>
===傳播途徑===
[[File:Bushmeat_-_Buschfleisch_Ghana.JPG|thumb]]（攝於2013年的[[加納|加納]]）。人類進食受污染之野味可感染包括伊波拉出血热在内的多種傳染病。<ref name=WHO_Fact_Sheet/>]]
<!--起始病例-->
雖只是一知半解，但專家相信與帶病動物或屍體的直接接觸為[[指示病例|指示病例]]出現之因。除了蝙蝠本身，黑猩猩、大猩猩、羚羊等野生動物，亦可因攝取了曾被蝙蝠啃咬的果實而沾染伊波拉病毒。<ref name="urlEbolavirus – Pathogen Safety Data Sheets">{{cite web | url = http://www.phac-aspc.gc.ca/lab-bio/res/psds-ftss/ebola-eng.php | title = Ebolavirus – Pathogen Safety Data Sheets | publisher = Public Health Agency of Canada | work =  | accessdate = 2015-02-21 | archive-date = 2017-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170620034820/http://www.phac-aspc.gc.ca/lab-bio/res/psds-ftss/ebola-eng.php | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=Gon2007>{{cite journal | author = Gonzalez JP, Pourrut X, Leroy E | title = Wildlife and Emerging Zoonotic Diseases: The Biology, Circumstances and Consequences of Cross-Species Transmission | journal = Current Topics in Microbiology and Immunology | volume = 315 | pages = 363–387|year= 2007 | pmid = 17848072 | doi = 10.1007/978-3-540-70962-6_15 | isbn = 978-3-540-70961-9 | series = Ebolavirus and other filoviruses }}</ref>豬隻、狗隻等家畜也有機會攜帶病原體。前者被證實有能力將病毒傳染給非人類的靈長動物，但後者卻並無此說且甚少出現病癥。<ref name="Weingartl_2013"/>

<!--人群間擴散-->
病毒絕少直接在天然宿主與人類群體間散播，而是通過首批患者的[[體液|體液]]傳染給其他人。<ref name="Funk2014">{{cite journal|author=Funk DJ, Kumar A|title=Ebola virus disease: an update for anesthesiologists and intensivists|journal=Can J Anaesth|volume=|issue=|pages=|date=11-2014|pmid=25373801|doi=10.1007/s12630-014-0257-z}}</ref><ref name="Drazen2014">{{cite journal|author=Drazen JM, Kanapathipillai R, Campion EW, Rubin EJ, Hammer SM, Morrissey S, Baden LR|title=Ebola and quarantine|journal=N Engl J Med|volume=371| issue=21|pages=2029–30|date=11-2014|pmid=25347231|doi=10.1056/NEJMe1413139}}</ref>病毒最常從患者的[[血液|血液]]、[[糞便|糞便]]與[[嘔吐|嘔吐物]]，通過[[鼻腔|鼻腔]]、[[口腔|口腔]]或[[傷口|傷口]]進入被感染者的體內。只有重症病人的[[唾液|唾液]]及大體積的呼吸道分泌物（如飛沫）具傳染性，不慎觸摸則有機會染病。<ref name=CDCNOV2014>{{cite web|title=How Ebola Is Spread|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/pdf/infections-spread-by-air-or-droplets.pdf|format=PDF|publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|date=01-11-2014|accessdate=2015-02-18|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022700/http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/pdf/infections-spread-by-air-or-droplets.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>接觸到受病毒污染的醫療器具（特別是針管）亦可致病<ref name="Chowell2014">{{cite journal|author=Chowell G, Nishiura H|title=Transmission dynamics and control of Ebola virus disease (EVD): a review|journal=BMC Med|volume=12|issue=1|pages=196|date=10-2014|pmid=25300956|pmc=4207625|doi=10.1186/s12916-014-0196-0|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4207625/|accessdate=2015-02-21|archive-date=2021-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211202232050/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4207625/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，故照顧伊波拉病人的醫護人員為高危人士<ref name=CDC2014QAT/>，特別是他們未有正確穿著保護衣物或沒有妥善處理醫療廢物。伊波拉病毒能在乾燥物件表面生存數小時，若伴隨體液的話則可達數天。<ref name=CDC2014QAT/>[[院內感染|院內感染]]的情況於一些醫療體系較不完善的非洲地區見怪不怪<ref>{{cite web|author=Tiaji Salaam-Blyther|title=The 2014 Ebola Outbreak: International and U.S. Responses|url=http://fas.org/sgp/crs/row/R43697.pdf|accessdate=2015-02-20|format=pdf|date=2014-08-26|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924045710/https://fas.org/sgp/crs/row/R43697.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，特別是他們重用已進行了皮下注射的針管<ref>{{cite book |editor1-last=Lashley |editor1-first=Felissa R. |editor2-last=Durham |editor2-first=Jerry D. |title=Emerging infectious diseases trends and issues |date=2007 |publisher=Springer |location=New York |isbn=9780826103505 |page=141 |edition=2nd |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=fsaWlKQ4OjcC&pg=PA141 |access-date=2014-08-16 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801065649/https://books.google.com/books?id=fsaWlKQ4OjcC&pg=PA141 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Hun2012/>。此烈性病潛伏期短，病發時，患者往往無法自由行動，使之易被警覺，故其在有能力進行完善隔離的醫學發達地區展開[[瘟疫|大規模流行]]的機會不大。<ref name=CDCPress2014>{{cite web|title=CDC Telebriefing on Ebola outbreak in West Africa|url=http://www.cdc.gov/media/releases/2014/t0728-ebola.html|website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|accessdate=2015-02-20|date=2014-07-28|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210142448/https://www.cdc.gov/media/releases/2014/t0728-ebola.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>男性患者的[[精液|精液]]在其康復後的7週內仍可攜帶病毒，並有機會透過[[性交|性交]]將之傳播；女性病人的[[母乳|乳汁]]亦然，惟暫不清楚何時方能進行安全餵哺。<ref name=WHO_Fact_Sheet/><ref name=CDCBreast2014/>除以上兩種情況外，痊癒者不再具傳染性。<ref name=CDC2014QAT/>

伊波拉病人的屍體同樣可傳播病毒。一些傳統的土葬或[[遺體保存技術|遺體保存技術]]，因涉及觸摸屍體故具一定風險。<ref name="Chan2014">{{cite journal | author = Chan M | title = Ebola virus disease in West Africa—no early end to the outbreak | journal = N Engl J Med | volume = 371 | issue = 13 | pages = 1183–5 | date = 09-2014 | pmid = 25140856 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMp1409859 | url = http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMp1409859 | accessdate = 2015-02-20 | archive-date = 2020-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200816131549/https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMp1409859 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

<!-- 焦點議題——空氣傳播 -->
目前沒有足夠的證據，顯示伊波拉病毒能通過空氣微粒於人類間傳播。<ref name=WHO_Transport/><ref name="Funk2014"/><ref name="Chowell2014"/>此傳染模式僅曾在設定了多項條件的猴子實驗裡出現。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Johnson E, Jaax N, White J, Jahrling P | title = Lethal experimental infections of rhesus monkeys by aerosolized Ebola virus | journal = International journal of experimental pathology | volume = 76 | issue = 4 | pages = 227–236 | date = Aug 1995 | pmid = 7547435 | pmc = 1997182 | issn = 0959-9673 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/7547435 | accessdate = 2015-02-20 | archive-date = 2020-05-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200502152403/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/7547435 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author = Leffel EK, Reed DS | title = Marburg and Ebola viruses as aerosol threats | journal = Biosecurity and bioterrorism : biodefense strategy, practice, and science | volume = 2 | issue = 3 | pages = 186–191 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15588056 | doi = 10.1089/bsp.2004.2.186 | issn = 1538-7135 | month =  }}</ref>另一項研究證實了豬隻能在不接觸的情況下將病毒傳染給猴子，但未能證明同樣的情況出現於猴子之間。<ref name="pmid23155478">{{cite journal |author = Weingartl HM, Embury-Hyatt C, Nfon C, Leung A, Smith G, Kobinger G | title = Transmission of Ebola virus from pigs to non-human primates | journal = Sci Rep | volume = 2 | issue = | pages = 811 | year = 2012 | pmid = 23155478 | pmc = 3498927 | doi = 10.1038/srep00811 }}</ref>不像豬隻，病毒多滋生於靈長動物的血液裡而非[[呼吸道|呼吸道]]表面，故後者無法通過咳嗽、打噴嚏的方式隔空傳播大量的病毒給其他個體。<ref name=sb1>{{cite journal|last1=Weingartl|first1=HM|last2=Embury-Hyatt|first2=C|last3=Nfon|first3=C|last4=Leung|first4=A|last5=Smith|first5=G|last6=Kobinger|first6=G|title=Transmission of Ebola virus from pigs to non-human primates.|journal=Scientific reports|date=2012|volume=2|pages=811|pmid=23155478|doi=10.1038/srep00811|pmc=3498927}}</ref>

==致病機理==
[[File:Ebola_Pathogenesis_in_Chinese.jpg|thumb]]
伊波拉出血熱的[[病理生理學|病理生理學]]為醫學界的熱門討論議題之一。伊波拉病毒主要透過粘膜處及表皮傷口入侵宿主身體。<ref name="Funk2014"/>它們能在多種細胞內進行高效繁殖，包括：[[單核細胞|單核細胞]]、[[巨噬細胞|巨噬細胞]]、[[內皮|內皮細胞]]、[[肝細胞|肝細胞]]、[[成纖維細胞|成纖維細胞]]、[[腎上腺|腎上腺細胞]]。<ref name="Ansari2014"/>這一過程會觸發[[細胞素風暴|細胞素風暴]]，導致[[敗血症|敗血症]]。<ref name="Tosh2014"/>巨噬細胞首當其衝受到影響，[[淋巴細胞|淋巴細胞]]後會一併進入[[細胞凋亡|細胞凋亡]]階段。<ref name="Chippaux2014">{{cite journal|author=Chippaux JP|title=Outbreaks of Ebola virus disease in Africa: the beginnings of a tragic saga|journal=J Venom Anim Toxins Incl Trop Dis|volume=20|issue=1|pages=44|date=10-2014|pmid=25320574|pmc=4197285|doi=10.1186/1678-9199-20-44}}</ref>因此，病人往往會出現{{link-en|淋巴細胞缺乏症|Lymphocytopenia}}及免疫力衰退。<ref name="Funk2014"/>病毒在數天後開始侵襲[[血管|血管]]內皮細胞，破壞[[血管|血管]]的凝聚。<ref name="Chippaux2014"/>負責處理{{link-en|細胞粘附|cell adhesion}}及細胞間結構的[[整合素|整合素]]，會隨著病毒[[糖蛋白|糖蛋白]]數量的上升而下降。<ref name="Goeijenbier2014"/>帶病者的肝臟亦受到破壞。<ref name="Goeijenbier2014"/>持續的[[出血|出血]]會導致[[水腫|水腫]]及[[血容量減少|低血容量休克]]。<ref name="isbn0-7910-8505-8">{{cite book |author=Smith, Tara |title=Ebola (Deadly Diseases and Epidemics) |publisher=Chelsea House Publications |location= |year=2005 |pages= |isbn=0-7910-8505-8 |oclc= |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>[[彌散性血管內凝血|彌散性血管內凝血]]常見於伊波拉病人身上。這是因病毒促使了單核及巨噬細胞分泌過剩的{{link-en|组织因子|Tissue factor}}，導致了血液凝固作用級聯。<ref name="Goeijenbier2014"/><ref name="doi10.1128/JVI.77.18.9733-9737.2003">{{cite journal | author = Sullivan N, Yang ZY, Nabel GJ | title = Ebola Virus Pathogenesis: Implications for Vaccines and Therapies | journal = Journal of Virology | volume = 77 | issue = 18 | pages = 9733–9737 | year = 2003 | pmid = 12941881 | pmc = 224575 | doi = 10.1128/JVI.77.18.9733-9737.2003 | url = http://jvi.asm.org/content/77/18/9733.full.pdf | format = Free full text | accessdate = 2015-02-24 | archive-date = 2018-07-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180723130449/http://jvi.asm.org/content/77/18/9733.full.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>

其中，[[先天免疫系統|先天性免疫力破壞]]為伊波拉致病機理的一大重點。<ref name="Misasi2014"/><ref name="Olejnik2011"/>病毒使患者身體無法對{{link-en|一型干擾素|Interferon type I}}（{{lang|la|α}} 與 {{lang|la|β}}）及[[干擾素伽瑪|二型干擾素伽瑪]]作出自然反應。<ref name="Kuhl2012"/><ref name="Ramanan2011">{{cite journal | author = Ramanan P, Shabman RS, Brown CS, Amarasinghe GK, Basler CF, Leung DW | title = Filoviral immune evasion mechanisms | journal = Viruses | volume = 3 | issue = 9 | pages = 1634–49 | date = 09-2011 | pmid = 21994800 | pmc = 3187693 | doi = 10.3390/v3091634 }}</ref>一般而言，數種位於宿主細胞[[細胞質基質|基質]]內、外的受體（主要為鐘形受體）會辨認出[[病原相關分子模式|病原相關分子]]，並進入活化階段。期間，{{link-en|干擾素控制因子|Interferon regulatory factors}}（3及7）觸發通信級聯，令一型干擾素表露並被釋放，使之與鄰近細胞表面的相關受體結合。<ref name="Kuhl2012"/>結合完成後，信使蛋白“{{lang|en|[[STAT1|STAT1]]}}”及“{{lang|en|[[STAT2|STAT2]]}}”被活化並轉移至[[細胞核|細胞核]]刺激{{link-en|干擾素激活性基因|Interferome}}，以製造出抗病毒蛋白。<ref name="Kuhl2012"/>伊波拉病毒（模式種）的“{{lang|en|V24}}”及“{{lang|en|VP35}}”蛋白，分別封鎖了“{{lang|en|STAT1}}”的去路及直接阻擋了{{lang|la|β}}干擾素的釋放。<ref name="Kuhl2012"/><ref name="Ramanan2011"/>通過抑制這些免疫反應，病毒能迅速蔓延至全身。<ref name="Chippaux2014"/>

==預防措施==
[[File:VHFisolation.png|thumb]]
避免接觸患者及帶病屍體的血液與分泌物、及早隔離及觀察帶病者、具備完善的疾病通報機制為基本的防疫條件。<ref name=CDC2014P>{{cite web|title=Ebola Hemorrhagic Fever Prevention|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/prevention/index.html|website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|accessdate=2015-02-24|date=2014-07-31|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116055739/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/prevention/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CDC1998>{{Cite book | last = Centers for Disease Control and Prevention and World Health Organization | title = Infection Control for Viral Haemorrhagic Fevers in the African Health Care Setting | url = http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/abroad/pdf/african-healthcare-setting-vhf.pdf | format = PDF | accessdate = 2015-02-24 | year = 1998 | publisher = Centers for Disease Control and Prevention | location = Atlanta, Georgia, US | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234447/http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/abroad/pdf/african-healthcare-setting-vhf.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>
