e-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109145135/https://www.osha.gov/SLTC/ebola/control_prevention.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

高溫或化學[[殺菌|消毒法]]能有效清除伊波拉病毒。持續至少30分鐘的60[[攝氏度|℃]]或5分鐘的100℃高溫可將病毒分解。 一些諸如[[酒精|酒精]]製品、洗潔精、漂白水（[[次氯酸鈉|次氯酸鈉]]）及漂白粉（[[次氯酸鈣|次氯酸鈣]]）等的表面清潔劑，在適當的濃度下同樣為有效的[[消毒|消毒]]用品。<ref name="Control Guidelines">{{cite web | url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/130596/1/WHO_HIS_SDS_2014.4_eng.pdf?ua=1&ua=1 | title=Infection Prevention and Control Guidance for Care of Patients with Suspected or Confirmed Filovirus Haemorrhagic Fever in Health-care Settings with Focus on Ebola | publisher=World Health Organization | date=08-2014 | accessdate=2015-02-24 | archive-date=2014-08-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821182137/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/130596/1/WHO_HIS_SDS_2014.4_eng.pdf?ua=1&ua=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="urlEbolavirus - Pathogen Safety Data Sheets">{{cite web | url = http://www.phac-aspc.gc.ca/lab-bio/res/psds-ftss/ebola-eng.php | title = Ebolavirus - Pathogen Safety Data Sheets | format =  | work = Laboratory Biosafety and Biosecurity > Biosafety Programs and Resources > Pathogen Safety Data Sheets and Risk Assessment | publisher = [[加拿大公共衛生局|Public Health Agency of Canada]] | accessdate = 2015-02-24 | archive-date = 2017-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170620034820/http://www.phac-aspc.gc.ca/lab-bio/res/psds-ftss/ebola-eng.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>勤加以清水及[[肥皂|肥皂]]洗手也是有效的防疫措施。<ref name="Gatherer 2014" />
[[叢林肉|叢林肉]]易沾染病毒且為人類感染伊波拉出血熱的源頭之一，故有關產物需在徹底煮熟後方能進食，亦不宜赤手觸摸。<ref name=WHO_Fact_Sheet/>傳統[[土葬|土葬]]殯儀涉及屍體觸碰，故應被勸阻或由[[人類學|社會人類學家]]協助改良。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.scidev.net/global/cooperation/feature/anthropologists-medics-ebola-guinea.html | title = How anthropologists help medics fight Ebola in Guinea | publisher = SciDev.Net | date = 2014 | accessdate = 2015-02-24 | author = Faye SL | archive-date = 2014-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006112752/http://www.scidev.net/global/cooperation/feature/anthropologists-medics-ebola-guinea.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=CDC2014P/><ref name=CDC1998/><ref name="url_www.who.int_ burial">{{cite web | url = http://www.who.int/csr/resources/publications/ebola/whoemcesr982sec7-9.pdf | title = Section 7: Use Safe Burial Practices | publisher = World Health Organization | work = Information resources on Ebola virus disease | date = 01-06-2014 | accessdate = 2015-02-24 | archive-date = 2015-02-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150226091100/http://www.who.int/csr/resources/publications/ebola/whoemcesr982sec7-9.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>

===公共衛生政策===
適當的公共衛生政策也是重要的一環。截至2014年8月，世衛認為旅遊禁令非為有效之防疫政策<ref>{{cite web|title=Air travel is low-risk for Ebola transmission|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/notes/2014/ebola-travel/en/|website=World Health Organization|date=2014-08-14|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-date=2015-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119231747/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/notes/2014/ebola-travel/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但飛機機組人員應按照指引，第一時間隔離並上報任何疑似案例<ref name=WHO_Transport/>。2014年10月，美國疾病預防中心制定了一套四級制的風險評估，衡量相關赴美人士罹患伊波拉出血熱的機會，以決定是否限制其活動。<ref name=CDC_monitor_movement>{{cite web |url=http://www.cdc.gov/media/releases/2014/fs1027-monitoring-symptoms-controlling-movement.html |title=Monitoring Symptoms and Controlling Movement to Stop Spread of Ebola |publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention |date=2014-10-27 |accessdate=2015-02-24 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204040335/https://www.cdc.gov/media/releases/2014/fs1027-monitoring-symptoms-controlling-movement.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><small>{{#tag:ref|此機制分“高風險（{{lang|en|High risk}}）”、“一般風險（{{lang|en|Some risk}}）”、“低風險（{{lang|en|Low [but not zero] risk}}）”及“無風險（{{lang|en|No risk}}）”四大級別，主要根據個人的旅遊史及健康狀況評定。當局建議處於“低風險”或更高級別的人士，接受為期21天的健康監察；處於“一般風險”的病人或會被實施旅遊及戶外活動限制；“高風險”人士則必須遵從有關限制。<ref name=CDC_monitor_movement/>|group=註|name=three}}</small>[[隔離檢疫|隔離檢疫]]（即強制隔離）將具傳染性的個體與正常人群分隔，能有效阻止伊波拉出血熱的擴散。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Sompayrac|first1=Lauren|title=How pathogenic viruses work|date=2002|publisher=Jones and Bartlett Publishers|location=Boston|isbn=9780763720827|page=87|edition=3. print.|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=PrOHLe35qNEC&pg=PA87|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-date=2014-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014073208/http://books.google.ca/books?id=PrOHLe35qNEC&pg=PA87|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pmid16597410">{{cite journal | author = Alazard-Dany N, Ottmann Terrangle M, Volchkov V | title = [Ebola and Marburg viruses: the humans strike back] | language = fr | journal = Med Sci (Paris) | volume = 22 | issue = 4 | pages = 405–10 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16597410 | doi = 10.1051/medsci/2006224405 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Schultz|first1=edited by Kristi Koenig, Carl|title=Koenig and Schultz's disaster medicine : comprehensive principles and practices|date=2009|publisher=[[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]]|location=Cambridge|isbn=9780521873673|page=209|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=IfpOtV-FAl4C&pg=PA209|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-date=2014-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014073915/http://books.google.ca/books?id=IfpOtV-FAl4C&pg=PA209|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{link-en|接触者追踪|contact trancing}}旨在尋找与感染者曾有密切接触的人士，並將之隔離以進行醫學測試及相應治療。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ebola 2014 — New Challenges, New Global Response and Responsibility|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMp1409903?query=featured_ebola|website=NEJM|publisher=[[新英格蘭醫學雜誌|''New England Journal of Medicine'']]|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-date=2014-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016053840/http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMp1409903?query=featured_ebola|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=What is Contact Tracing?|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/pdf/contact-tracing.pdf|website=CDC|publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115230302/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/pdf/contact-tracing.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==診斷方式==
患者的[[病史|病史]]對診斷伊波拉出血熱極為重要。
===實驗室診斷===
{{link-en|血小板减少症|Thrombocytopenia}}、肝細胞[[谷丙轉氨酶|谷丙轉氨酶]]與[[天冬氨酸氨基轉移酶|天冬氨酸氨基轉移酶]]的上升、血凝力失常（多伴隨著[[彌散性血管內凝血|彌散性血管內凝血]]）、[[白細胞减少症|白細胞减少症]]與{{link-en|白細胞增生症|Leukocytosis}}的先後出現，均為診斷伊波拉出血熱的非針對性指標。<ref name="Kortepeter2011">{{cite journal | author = Kortepeter MG, Bausch DG, Bray M | title = Basic clinical and laboratory features of filoviral hemorrhagic fever | journal = J Infect Dis | volume = 204 | issue = Supplement 3 | pages = S810–6 | date = 11-2011 | pmid = 21987756 | doi = 10.1093/infdis/jir299 | url = http://jid.oxfordjournals.org/content/204/suppl_3/S810.long | accessdate = 2015-02-24 | archive-date = 2015-01-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150104122512/http://jid.oxfordjournals.org/content/204/suppl_3/S810.long | dead-url = no }}</ref>

針對性測試方面，若病人血液樣本被驗出含有病毒、病毒的[[核糖核酸|核糖核酸]]或[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]、相關[[抗體|抗體]]的話，即被確診感染伊波拉病毒。[[細胞培養|細胞培養]]病毒測試法、[[聚合酶鏈式反應|聚合酶鏈式反應]]病毒核糖核酸測試法、[[酶聯免疫吸附試驗|酶聯免疫吸附試驗]]病毒蛋白測試法於早期病患者及屍體身上較為有效，而抗體測試法則適用於後期病人或痊癒者。<ref name=CDC2014Diag>{{cite web|title=Ebola Hemorrhagic Fever Diagnosis|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/diagnosis/index.html|website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|accessdate=2015-02-24|date=2014-01-28|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116062940/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/diagnosis/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>絲狀病毒（包括伊波拉病毒）因具有獨特蟲狀構造而容易透過[[電子顯微鏡|電子顯微鏡]]辨認，惟此無法進一步鑑定具體種類。<ref name=Geisbert1995/>疾病爆發期間，提取病毒的測試方式不太適用。故聚合酶鏈式反應及酶聯免疫吸附試驗為實地檢查或流動醫院中，最常用之診斷方法。<ref name="pmid16267962">{{cite journal |author = Grolla A, Lucht A, Dick D, Strong JE, Feldmann H | title = Laboratory diagnosis of Ebola and Marburg hemorrhagic fever | journal = Bull Soc Pathol Exot | volume = 98 | issue = 3 | pages = 205–9 | year = 2005 | pmid = 16267962 | doi =  }}</ref>2014年於[[利比里亞|利比里亞]]推行的新型流動測試設備，能在樣本呈交後的3-5小時之內給予結果。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.who.int/features/2014/liberia-mobile-ebola-lab/en/ |title=Liberia: New Ebola mobile lab speeds up diagnosis and improves care, |date=2014 |website=WHO.int |publisher=World Health Organization |accessdate=2015-02-24 |archive-date=2014-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024235048/http://who.int/features/2014/liberia-mobile-ebola-lab/en/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===鑑別診斷===
伊波拉出血熱病癥與{{link-en|馬爾堡出血熱|Marburg virus disease}}的如出一轍。<ref name="Harrison">{{Cite book |title=Harrison's Principles of Internal Medicine | publisher=McGraw-Hill |last1=Longo |first1=DL | last2=Kasper | first2=DL | last3=Jameson |first3=JL |last4=Hauser |first4=SL | last5=Loscalzo |first5=J | year=2012 | chapter=Chapter 197 | edition=18th | isbn=0-07-174889-X }}</ref>其亦容易與其他一些常見於非洲赤道地區的疾病混為一談（如：其他的[[病毒性出血熱|病毒性出血熱]]、[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]、[[傷寒|傷寒]]、[[志賀桿菌病|志賀桿菌病]]、[[立克次體|立克次體病]]（尤其是[[斑疹傷寒|斑疹傷寒]]、[[霍亂|霍亂]]、[[革蘭氏陰性菌|革蘭氏陰性菌]][[敗血症|敗血症]]）及諸如[[回歸熱|回歸熱]]及[[腸道出血性大腸桿菌|出血性腸道炎]]等的[[萊姆病|萊姆病]]）。除此，[[鉤端螺旋體病|鉤端螺旋體病]]、[[恙蟲病|恙蟲病]]、[[鼠疫|鼠疫]]、[[Q型流感|Q型流感]]、[[念珠菌病|念珠菌病]]、[[組織胞漿菌病|組織胞漿菌病]]、{{link-en|錐蟲病|Trypanosomiasis}}、[[器官|器官]][[利甚曼病|利甚曼病]]、出血性[[天花|天花]]、[[麻疹|麻疹]]和急性重症型[[病毒性肝炎|病毒性肝炎]]亦位列鑑別診斷的名單上。<ref>{{cite web |title=Viral Hemorrhagic Fever |url=http://www.sfcdcp.org/document.html?id=316 |website=San Francisco Department of Public Health |publisher=Communicable Disease Control and Prevention |accessdate=2015-02-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924100807/http://www.sfcdcp.org/document.html?id=316 |archivedate=2015-09-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>有機會與伊波拉出血熱混淆的{{link-en|非傳染性疾病|Non-communicable disease}}有：[[急性早幼粒細胞白血病|急性早幼粒細胞白血病]]、[[溶血性尿毒綜合症|溶血性尿毒綜合症]]、蛇咬中毒、[[凝固作用|凝血因子]]缺乏症/血小板疾病、{{link-en|血栓性血小板減少紫斑症|Thrombotic thrombocytopenic purpura}}、[[遺傳性出血性血管擴張症|遺傳性出血性血管擴張症]]、[[川崎氏病|川崎氏病]]，以及[[華法林|華法林]]中毒。<ref name=Gear1989>{{cite journal | author = Gear JH | title = Clinical aspects of African viral hemorrhagic fevers | journal = Reviews of infectious diseases | volume = 11 Suppl 4 | pages = S777–S782 | year = 1989 | pmid = 2665013 | doi=10.1093/clinids/11.supplement_4.s777}}</ref><ref name=Gear1978>{{cite journal | author = Gear JH, Ryan J, Rossouw E | title = A consideration of the diagnosis of dangerous infectious fevers in South Africa | journal = South African medical journal = Suid-Afrikaanse tydskrif vir geneeskunde | volume = 53 | issue = 7 | pages = 235–237 | year = 1978 | pmid = 565951 }}</ref><ref name=Grolla2005>{{cite journal |author = Grolla A, Lucht A, Dick D, Strong JE, Feldmann H | title = Laboratory diagnosis of Ebola and Marburg hemorrhagic fever | journal = Bulletin de la Societe de pathologie exotique (1990) | volume = 98 | issue = 3 | pages = 205–209 | year = 2005 | pmid = 16267962 }}</ref><ref name=Bogomolov1998>{{cite journal |author = Bogomolov BP | title = Differential diagnosis of infectious diseases with hemorrhagic syndrome | journal = Terapevticheskii arkhiv | volume = 70 | issue = 4 | pages = 63–68 | year = 1998 | pmid = 9612907 }}</ref>

==病情監控==
目前尚未有針對性的伊波拉治療方案，所有的措施均旨在舒緩疾病所帶來的傷害及降低併發症的風險。<ref name=Choi-2013/>[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]亦呼籲大眾要提防假冒產品。<ref>{{cite web|title=FDA warns consumers about fraudulent Ebola treatment products|url=http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm410086.htm|accessdate=2015-02-25|publisher=[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|Food and Drug Administration]]|archive-date=2014-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819083214/http://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm410086.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Inspections, Compliance, Enforcement, and Criminal Investigations|url=http://www.fda.gov/ICECI/EnforcementActions/WarningLetters/2014/ucm416051.htm|publisher=Food and Drug Administration|accessdate=2015-02-25|archive-date=2014-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008213137/http://www.fda.gov/ICECI/EnforcementActions/WarningLetters/2014/ucm416051.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===標準看護===
及早接受{{link-en|口服補液治療|Oral rehydration therapy}}或[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]等舒緩性療法，有助提升存活率。<ref name=WHO_Fact_Sheet/>這包括了痛楚控制、體溫控制、止吐、抗憂鬱。於發病早期注射[[抗凝劑|抗凝劑]]（如[[肝素|肝素]]）可減少[[彌散性血管內凝血|彌散性血管內凝血]]的危害；而在後期注射[[凝固作用|凝固劑]]則可降低[[出血|出血]]的程度。另外，[[抗生素|抗生素]]有助杜絕由[[細菌|細菌]]或[[真菌|真菌]]（於已受伊波拉病毒破壞之器官）所引起的[[機會性感染|繼發性感染]]。<ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite journal | author = Bausch DG, Feldmann H, Geisbert TW, Bray M, Sprecher AG, Boumandouki P, Rollin PE, Roth C | title = Outbreaks of Filovirus Hemorrhagic Fever: Time to Refocus on the Patient | journal = The Journal of Infectious Diseases | volume = 196 | pages = S136–S141 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17940941 | doi = 10.1086/520542 | author9 = Winnipeg Filovirus Clinical Working Group }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite journal |author = Jeffs B | title = A clinical guide to viral haemorrhagic fevers: Ebola, Marburg and Lassa | journal = Tropical Doctor | volume = 36 | issue = 1 | pages = 1–4 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16483416 | doi = 10.1258/004947506775598914 }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated3>{{cite journal |author = Nkoghé D, Formenty P, Nnégué S, Mvé MT, Hypolite I, Léonard P, Leroy E, Comité International de Coordination Technique et Scientifique | title = Practical guidelines for the management of Ebola infected patients in the field | journal = Medecine tropicale : revue du Corps de sante colonial | volume = 64 | issue = 2 | pages = 199–204 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15460155 }}</ref>世衛呼籲避免使用[[阿斯匹林|阿斯匹林]]及[[布洛芬|布洛芬]]這兩種容易導致出血的藥物止痛。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ebola messages for the general public|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/131682/1/9789241548847_eng.pdf?ua=1|publisher=World Health Organization|date=2014|accessdate=2015-02-25|page=11|quote=Do not give aspirin or any other pain killer.|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307195046/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/131682/1/9789241548847_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{link-en|濃縮紅血球血包|Packed red blood cells}}、[[血小板|血小板]]及{{link-en|冰凍血漿|Fresh frozen plasma}}一類的血液製品，在必要時也可一併使用。<ref name=Clark_2012>{{cite journal | author = Clark DV, Jahrling PB, Lawler JV | title = Clinical management of filovirus-infected patients | journal = Viruses | volume = 4 | issue = 9 | pages = 1668–86 |date=September 2012 | pmid = 23170178 | pmc = 3499825 | doi = 10.3390/v4091668 }}</ref>

根據世衛指引，提供家中護理者宜使用已吸收[[氯|氯水]]的毛巾移動病人或屍體，並以乾淨的毛巾遮掩口鼻。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.who.int/csr/disease/ebola/Annex_18_risk_reduction_home_care.pdf?ua=1|title=Annex 18. Transmission risk reduction of filoviruses in home-care settings|work=Ebola and Marburg virus disease epidemics: preparedness, alert, control, and evaluation Interim manual version 1.2 CHAPTER 7 ANNEXES|accessdate=2015-02-25|archive-date=2014-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026092619/http://www.who.int/csr/disease/ebola/Annex_18_risk_reduction_home_care.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===深切治療===
[[已發展國家|已發展國家]]一般可為病人提供[[紧急监护医学|深切治療]]。<ref name="Feldmann2011"/>首要工作為保持患者[[體液|體液]]及[[電解質|電解質]]的平衡，以降低[[脫水|脫水]]對身體帶來的影響。[[血液透析|血液透析]]與[[體外膜氧合|體外膜氧合]]則可分別解決[[腎衰竭|腎衰竭]]及肺功能下降的問題。<ref name="Feldmann2011"/>

==預後==
罹患伊波拉出血熱的綜合死亡率位於25-90%之間，平均值為五成（模式種病毒的威脅則更高）。<ref name=WHO_Fact_Sheet/><ref name="Elsevier/Academic Press"/>臨床實例證明，持續感染會造成長期的後遺症，如：[[睾丸炎|睾丸炎]]、[[關節疼痛|關節疼痛]]、[[肌肉疼痛|肌肉疼痛]]、{{link-en|脫屑|Desquamation}}、[[脫髮|脫髮]]及多種眼部症狀（[[畏光|畏光]]、{{link-en|溢淚|Epiphora (medicine)}}、[[葡萄膜炎|葡萄膜炎]]、{{link-en|脈絡膜視網膜炎|Chorioretinitis}}，甚至[[失明|失明]]）。<ref name=WHO_Fact_Sheet/>除此，康復者大多都會出現慢性肌肉與關節疼痛、[[肝炎|肝炎]]、聽力下降以及諸如長期疲勞、胃口下降、無法恢復體重等的全身症狀。<ref name=Hun2012/><ref name="Tosh2014">{{cite journal|author=Tosh PK, Sampathkumar P|title=What Clinicians Should Know About the 2014 Ebola Outbreak|journal=Mayo Clin Proc|volume=89|issue=12|pages=1710–17|date=12-2014|pmid=25467644|doi=10.1016/j.mayocp.2014.10.010}}</ref>

==流行概況==
[[File:EbolaSubmit2.png|thumb]]
{{See also|伊波拉出血熱爆發列表}}
伊波拉出血熱常間歇性地出現於[[撒哈拉以南非洲|非洲撒哈拉以南的地區]]，走向風裡楊花。從1976年（人類首次發現此病）至2013年為止，[[世衛|世衛]]一共公佈了2,387宗確診個案，共24次爆發，總死亡人數為1,590名。<ref name=WHO_Fact_Sheet/><ref name=CDC_MM_Weekly_Report/>最具規模的一次流行，為2014-16年的[[西非伊波拉病毒疫症|西非疫症]]。

