====蘇丹====
人類史上第一宗伊波拉出血熱確診個案，出現於現在的[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]（當時的[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]）一個名為“{{link-en|恩扎拉|Nzara, South Sudan}}”的村落。<ref name="Hoenen2012"/><ref name="Peterson AT, Bauer JT, Mills JN 2004 40–47">{{cite journal | author = Peterson AT, Bauer JT, Mills JN | title = Ecologic and Geographic Distribution of Filovirus Disease | journal = Emerging Infectious Diseases | volume = 10 | issue = 1 | pages = 40–47 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15078595 | pmc = 3322747 | doi = 10.3201/eid1001.030125 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author = Bennett D, Brown D | title = Ebola virus | journal = BMJ (Clinical research ed.) | volume = 310 | issue = 6991 | pages = 1344–1345 | date = May 1995 | pmid = 7787519 | pmc = 2549737 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.310.6991.1344 }}</ref>該病人為當地一家棉織廠的主人。他於6月27日發病，三天后入院，並在7月6日死亡。<ref name="Feldmann2011"/><ref name="who's first encounter">{{cite web|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/bulletin/1978/Vol56-No2/bulletin_1978_56(2)_247-270.pdf|title=Ebola haemorrhagic fever in Sudan, 1976|format=pdf|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013194802/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/bulletin/1978/Vol56-No2/bulletin_1978_56(2)_247-270.pdf|archivedate=2014-10-13|accessdate=2015-02-10}}</ref>引發此次爆發的元兇，為最終奪取了151人性命（總患病人數為284名）的蘇丹病毒。雖然世衛人員知道他們面對的是一種新型疾病，但在相隔數月後的扎伊爾爆發中，病原體才被深入了解及命名。<ref name="who's first encounter"/>
====扎伊爾====
同年8月26日，現在的[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]（當時的[[扎伊爾|扎伊爾]]）北部[[蒙加拉省|蒙加拉省]]的[[亚布库|亚布库]]村莊，爆發了伊波拉出血熱。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Hewlett|first1=Barry|last2=Hewlett|first2=Bonnie|title=Ebola, Culture and Politics: The Anthropology of an Emerging Disease|date=2007|publisher=Cengage Learning|page=103|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=aboFAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA103&lpg=PA103&dq=congo+yambuku&source=bl&ots=pBDyVznpfn&sig=_6uTpL46YKgFJmniEMIo2G5Um3I&hl=en&sa=X&ei=SKDaU9-ONtKj8gGK74DYAQ&ved=0CEMQ6AEwBzgK#v=onepage&q=congo%20yambuku&f=false|accessdate=2015-02-25|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107075401/https://books.google.com/books?id=aboFAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA103&lpg=PA103&dq=congo+yambuku&source=bl&ots=pBDyVznpfn&sig=_6uTpL46YKgFJmniEMIo2G5Um3I&hl=en&sa=X&ei=SKDaU9-ONtKj8gGK74DYAQ#v=onepage&q=congo%20yambuku&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Feldmann2003>{{cite journal | author = Feldmann H, Jones S, Klenk HD, Schnittler HJ | title = Ebola virus: from discovery to vaccine | journal = Nature Reviews. Immunology | volume = 3 | issue = 8 | pages = 677–85 | date = 08-2003 | pmid = 12974482 | doi = 10.1038/nri1154 |}}</ref>[[指示病例|首名患者]]是當地一所學校的校長。他早前於8月12至22日期間，到[[伊波拉河|伊波拉河]]接近[[中非共和國|中非共和國]]的邊沿地帶旅行，回家後在8月26日出現症狀。<ref name="whqlibdoc.who.int">{{cite journal | author =  | title = Ebola haemorrhagic fever in Zaire, 1976 | journal = Bull. World Health Organ. | volume = 56 | issue = 2 | pages = 271–93 | year = 1978 | pmid = 307456 | pmc = 2395567 | doi =  | url = http://whqlibdoc.who.int/bulletin/1978/Vol56-No2/bulletin_1978_56(2)_271-293.pdf | accessdate = 2015-02-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808213715/http://whqlibdoc.who.int/bulletin/1978/Vol56-No2/bulletin_1978_56%282%29_271-293.pdf | archivedate = 2014-08-08 }}</ref>起初，有關衛生所對此病例不以為然，列作[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]處理，分配了[[奎寧|奎寧]]作治療藥物。可是，他的病情持續惡化，最終於9月5日被送入當地的教會醫院，至發病後的第14天（即9月8日）病逝。<ref name="urlOutbreak of Ebola Viral Hemorrhagic Fever – Zaire, 1995">{{cite journal | url = http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/00037078.htm | title = Outbreak of Ebola Viral Hemorrhagic Fever – Zaire, 1995 | journal = Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report | volume = 44 | issue = 19 | pages = 381–2 | year = 1995 | access-date = 2015-02-10 | archive-date = 2020-11-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201104112022/https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/00037078.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="urlMabalo Lokela Archives – Political Moll">{{cite web | url = http://politicalmoll.com/tag/mabalo-lokela/ | title = Ebola: The Truth Behind The Outbreak (Video) l | author = Elezra M | work = Mabalo Lokela Archives – Political Mol | accessdate = 2015-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150712140500/http://politicalmoll.com/tag/mabalo-lokela/ | archive-date = 2015-07-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>多名與這位校長有近距離接觸的人士先後出現症狀，並陸續死亡，全村陷入恐慌。<ref name="whqlibdoc.who.int"/><ref name=Piot_2012>{{cite book | author = Piot P, Marshall R | title = No time to lose: a life in pursuit of deadly viruses | url = https://archive.org/details/notimetoloselife0000piot | year = 2012 | publisher = W.W. Norton & Co. | location = New York | isbn = 978-0393063165 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/notimetoloselife0000piot/page/30 30], 90 | edition = 1st }}</ref><ref name="Piot-one">{{cite news | author =Peter Piot | title =Part one: A virologist's tale of Africa's first encounter with Ebola | quote = | newspaper =ScienceInsider | date =11 August 2014 | pages = | url =http://news.sciencemag.org/africa/2014/08/part-one-virologists-tale-africas-first-encounter-ebola | accessdate =2015-02-10 | archive-date =2014-10-09 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20141009050901/http://news.sciencemag.org/africa/2014/08/part-one-virologists-tale-africas-first-encounter-ebola | dead-url =no }}Free access</ref><ref name="Piot-two">{{cite news | author =Peter Piot | title =Part two: A virologist's tale of Africa's first encounter with Ebola | quote = | newspaper =ScienceInsider | date =2014-08-13 | pages = | url =http://news.sciencemag.org/africa/2014/08/part-two-virologists-tale-africas-first-encounter-ebola | accessdate =2015-02-10 | archive-date =2014-11-16 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20141116233325/http://news.sciencemag.org/africa/2014/08/part-two-virologists-tale-africas-first-encounter-ebola | dead-url =no }}</ref>當地衛生局及時任扎伊爾總統的[[蒙博托·塞塞·塞科|蒙博托·塞塞·塞科]]宣布，將包括國都[[金沙薩|金沙薩]]在內的有關地區劃為檢疫區，禁止外人進入，另對水、陸、空運輸實施[[戒嚴|戒嚴]]。[[美國疾病控制與預防中心|美國疾病控制與預防中心]]的研究員[[彼得·皮奥特|彼得·皮奥特]]在視察該地時指出，當地的比利時修女使用了未經徹底消毒的針管為孕婦注射多餘的[[維他命|維他命]]，無意地促成了這次流行。疾病爆發期間，恩戈伊·莫索拉（{{lang|en|Ngoy Mushola}}）醫生首度為此病作出了臨床描述：“罹患這病的典型特徵為：39[[攝氏度|℃]]或以上的高燒、[[吐血|吐血]]、便血、胸骨下腹痛、關節“重感”、虛脫及以平均三天的速度死亡。”<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bardi|first1=Jason Socrates|title=Death Called a River|url=http://www.scripps.edu/newsandviews/e_20020114/ebola1.html|website=The Scripps Research Institute|accessdate=2015-02-25|quote=The illness is characterized with a high temperature of about 39°C, hematemesis, diarrhea with blood, retrosternal abdominal pain, prostration with "heavy" articulations, and rapid evolution death after a mean of three days.|archive-date=2014-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802170848/http://www.scripps.edu/newsandviews/e_20020114/ebola1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>起先，元兇被誤認為是形態相似的[[馬爾堡病毒|馬爾堡病毒]]，後發現其乃前所未見的新型種，並與早前的蘇丹爆發有所關聯（時下各種伊波拉病毒尚未被劃分）。專家以位於亞布庫（此病最早的爆發確認點）附近的伊波拉河為依據，將此病原體定名為“伊波拉病毒”。<ref name=Feldmann2011/><small>{{#tag:ref|暫不清楚是以卡爾·約翰遜為首的美國疾病中心的團隊，抑或是有關的比利時研究隊才是最初的命名者（兩者均有獲引述）。<ref name="hz">{{cite book| title=The Hot Zone | url=https://archive.org/details/hotzone00rich |last=Preston |first=Richard |page=[https://archive.org/details/hotzone00rich/page/117 117] |quote=Karl Johnson named it Ebola |publisher=Anchor Books (Random House) |date=1995-07-20}}</ref>|group=註|name=four}}</small>疾病爆發最終在26天後，因隔離檢疫生效及防疫意識上升而結束，檢疫期為時2週。<ref name=Stimola>{{cite book | author = Stimola A | title = Ebola | url = https://archive.org/details/ebola0000stim | year = 2011 | publisher = Rosen Pub. | location = New York | isbn = 978-1435894334 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/ebola0000stim/page/31 31], 52 | edition = 1st }}</ref>此次的流行由模式種病毒引起，最終在318位感染者中奪取了280人的性命。<ref name=ZaireEHF>{{cite journal|title=Ebola haemorrhagic fever in Zaire, 1976|pages=271–293|issn=0042-9686|journal=Bulletin of the World Health Organization|volume=56|issue=2|date=1978|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/307456|accessdate=2019-02-12|pmid=307456|pmc=PMC2395567|archive-date=2020-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502150813/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/307456|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="emedicine.com">{{cite web | url = http://www.emedicine.com/MED/topic626.htm | accessdate = 06-10-2008 | author = King JW | title = Ebola Virus | date = 02-04-2008 | work = eMedicine | publisher = WebMd | archive-date = 2008-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080928063653/http://www.emedicine.com/med/TOPIC626.HTM | dead-url = no }}</ref>

