伊波拉出血熱在相隔多年後死灰復燃。<ref name=CDC_order/>繼1979年再次侵襲蘇丹後，又在1994年首次出現於[[加蓬|加蓬]]<ref name="PMID9988167">{{cite journal|title=Ebola hemorrhagic fever outbreaks in Gabon, 1994-1997: epidemiologic and health control issues|pages=S65–75|issn=0022-1899|journal=The Journal of Infectious Diseases|volume=179 Suppl 1|date=1999-2|doi=10.1086/514290|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9988167|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=A. J. Georges, E. M. Leroy, A. A. Renaut, C. T. Benissan, R. J. Nabias, M. T. Ngoc, P. I. Obiang, J. P. Lepage, E. J. Bertherat, D. D. Bénoni, E. J. Wickings, J. P. Amblard, J. M. Lansoud-Soukate, J. M. Milleliri, S. Baize, M. C. Georges-Courbot|pmid=9988167|archive-date=2020-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502093457/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9988167|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2000年蔓延至[[烏干達|烏干達]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=An outbreak of Ebola in Uganda|pages=1068–1075|issn=1360-2276|journal=Tropical medicine & international health: TM & IH|volume=7|issue=12|date=2002-12|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12460399|accessdate=2019-02-13|author=S. I. Okware, F. G. Omaswa, S. Zaramba, A. Opio, J. J. Lutwama, J. Kamugisha, E. B. Rwaguma, P. Kagwa, M. Lamunu|pmid=12460399|archive-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106004836/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12460399|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2003年的[[剛果共和國|剛果共和國]]爆發錄得了至今最高的伊波拉病死率——143名病患者中的128人死亡（致死率為90%）。<ref name="pmid14579469">{{cite journal |author = Formenty P, Libama F, Epelboin A, Allarangar Y, Leroy E, Moudzeo H, Tarangonia P, Molamou A, Lenzi M, Ait-Ikhlef K, Hewlett B, Roth C, Grein T | title = [Outbreak of Ebola hemorrhagic fever in the Republic of the Congo, 2003: a new strategy?] | language = fr | journal = Med Trop (Mars) | volume = 63 | issue = 3 | pages = 291–5 | year = 2003 | pmid = 14579469 | doi = }}</ref>模式種及蘇丹種病毒其後間歇性地出現於以上各地。<ref name=CDC_order>{{cite web|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/resources/outbreak-table.html|title=Known Cases and Outbreaks of Ebola Hemorrhagic Fever, in Chronological Order|date=2014-08-30|accessdate=2015-02-25|publisher=National Center for Infectious Diseases & Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|archive-date=2015-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127123214/http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/resources/outbreak-table.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外，一種名為“本迪布焦病毒”的新型伊波拉病毒，在2007年的西烏干達[[本迪布焦區|本迪布焦區]]爆發中首度亮相。<ref name="PMID19023410">{{cite journal|title=Newly discovered ebola virus associated with hemorrhagic fever outbreak in Uganda|pages=e1000212|issn=1553-7374|journal=PLoS pathogens|volume=4|issue=11|date=2008-11|doi=10.1371/journal.ppat.1000212|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19023410|accessdate=2019-02-12|author=Jonathan S. Towner, Tara K. Sealy, Marina L. Khristova, César G. Albariño, Sean Conlan, Serena A. Reeder, Phenix-Lan Quan, W. Ian Lipkin, Robert Downing, Jordan W. Tappero, Samuel Okware, Julius Lutwama, Barnabas Bakamutumaho, John Kayiwa, James A. Comer, Pierre E. Rollin, Thomas G. Ksiazek, Stuart T. Nichol|pmid=19023410|pmc=PMC2581435|archive-date=2020-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502041936/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19023410|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WHO-PR20080220">{{Cite press release|title=End of Ebola outbreak in Uganda|publisher=World Health Organization|date=2008-02-20|url=http://www.who.int/csr/don/2007_02_20b/en/index.html|accessdate=2015-02-25|archive-date=2013-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027040637/http://www.who.int/csr/don/2007_02_20b/en/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

