西非疫症乃伊波拉出血熱有史以來最嚴重的一次爆發，亦是該病首次登陸西非。<ref name=CDC_order/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMp1409903?query=featured_home&|title=Ebola 2014 — New Challenges, New Global Response and Responsibility|publisher=The New England Journal of Medicine|accessdate=2015-02-25|archive-date=2015-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101234836/http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMp1409903?query=featured_home&|dead-url=no}}</ref>一名於2013年12月6日死亡的嬰兒或為是此流行的源頭。<ref>{{Cite news| issn = 0362-4331| last = Grady| first = Denise| author2 = Sheri Fink| title = Tracing Ebola’s Breakout to an African 2-Year-Old| work = ''The New York Times''| accessdate = 2015-02-25| date = 09-08-2014| url = http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/10/world/africa/tracing-ebolas-breakout-to-an-african-2-year-old.html| archive-date = 2014-08-10| archive-url = https://archive.today/20140810183242/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/10/world/africa/tracing-ebolas-breakout-to-an-african-2-year-old.html?_r=0| dead-url = no}}</ref>疫症一發不可收拾。[[畿內亞|畿內亞]]於2014年的3月，由世衛確認出現首宗病例；8月底，疾病已蔓延至[[尼日利亞|尼日利亞]]及[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]。<ref name=WHO-ebola-rpt>{{cite news |url=http://apps.who.int/ebola/ |work=Epidemic & Pandemic Alert and Response (EPR) – Outbreak News |title=Ebola Page |publisher=World Health Organization |accessdate=2015-02-25 |archive-date=2018-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815050944/http://apps.who.int/ebola/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年8月8日，世衛宣布此次爆發為“國際突發性公共衛生事件”，並呼籲各國積極及迅速協助受影響地區。<ref>{{cite news | title = WHO raises global alarm over Ebola outbreak | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/ebola-outbreak-international-public-health-emergency-who/ | accessdate = 2015-02-25 | work = CBS | archive-date = 2014-08-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808095616/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/ebola-outbreak-international-public-health-emergency-who/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="WHOemergency">{{cite news|title=Ebola epidemic in West Africa declared a health emergency|url=http://www.bignewsnetwork.com/index.php/sid/224572421|accessdate=2015-02-25|publisher=''Big News Network.com''|archive-date=2014-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224173009/http://www.bignewsnetwork.com/index.php/sid/224572421|dead-url=no}}</ref>相關[[陸軍|陸軍]]封鎖了疫區，防止病毒進一步擴散。<ref name="CordonAreas">{{cite news | title = Using a Tactic Unseen in a Century, Countries Cordon Off Ebola-Racked Areas | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/13/science/using-a-tactic-unseen-in-a-century-countries-cordon-off-ebola-racked-areas.html | accessdate = 2015-02-25 | work = ''The New York Times'' | archive-date = 2014-08-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140814041354/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/13/science/using-a-tactic-unseen-in-a-century-countries-cordon-off-ebola-racked-areas.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>8月中旬，[[無國界醫生|無國界醫生]]表示，利比里亞首都[[蒙羅維亞|蒙羅維亞]]的情況為“災難性”及“每況愈下”。當地醫療系統運作癱瘓，工作人員處於恐慌之中，很多罹患其他疾病的人士未能得到及時的看護<ref name="Common Dreams ">{{cite web | url=http://www.commondreams.org/news/2014/08/18/liberias-ebola-stricken-villages-residents-face-stark-choices | title=In Liberia's Ebola-Stricken Villages, Residents Face 'Stark' Choices | publisher=Common Dreams | work=Liberia's Ebola-Stricken Villages, Residents Face 'Stark' Choices | date=2014-08-18 | accessdate=2015-02-25 | archive-date=2014-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140820041111/http://www.commondreams.org/news/2014/08/18/liberias-ebola-stricken-villages-residents-face-stark-choices | dead-url=no }}</ref>；逾百位醫護人員殉職<ref>{{cite web|title=Unprecedented number of medical staff infected with Ebola|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/ebola/25-august-2014/en/|website=WHO|accessdate=2014-08-29|date=2014-08-25|archive-date=2014-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828123825/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/ebola/25-august-2014/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。世衛於9月26日的報告中總結：“西非伊波拉疫症是人類當代最嚴重且緊急的一次公共衛生危機。即便是其他第四類生物危險品亦沒有如此迅速、持續地感染多個地區的人們。”<ref name="Ebola situation assessment ">{{cite web | url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/ebola/26-september-2014/en/ | title=Experimental therapies: growing interest in the use of whole blood or plasma from recovered Ebola patients (convalescent therapies) | publisher=World Health Organization | date=2014-09-26 | accessdate=2015-02-25 | quote=The Ebola epidemic ravaging parts of West Africa is the most severe acute public health emergency seen in modern times. Never before in recorded history has a biosafety level four pathogen infected so many people so quickly, over such a broad geographical area, for so long. | archive-date=2014-09-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140928143036/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/ebola/26-september-2014/en/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>{{#section:西非伊波拉病毒疫症|casesasof}}，是次爆發已有{{#section:西非伊波拉病毒疫症|cases}}宗疑似個案被上報，共{{#section:西非伊波拉病毒疫症|deaths}}宗死亡案例被證實{{#section:西非伊波拉病毒疫症|caserefs}}，惟此或低於實際情況<ref name="CDC Estimating future number of cases">{{cite journal | url=http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/su63e0923a1.htm | title=Estimating the Future Number of Cases in the Ebola Epidemic — Liberia and Sierra Leone, 2014–2015 | journal=Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report | publisher=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention | location=United States | date=2014-09-26 | author=Meltzer, Martin I. | author2=Atkins, Charisma Y. | author3=Santibanez, Scott | author4=Knust, Barbara | author5=Petersen, Brett W. | author6=Ervin, Elizabeth D. | author7=Nichol, Stuart T. | author8=Damon, Inger K. | author9=Washington, Michael L. | display-authors=3 | accessdate=2015-02-25 | archive-date=2015-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131015327/http://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/su63e0923a1.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

除了人命傷亡，疫症亦造成了經濟損失及社會動盪。《[[金融時報|金融時報]]》一篇報告指出，由疾病引發之資源短缺問題造成了比病毒本身更大的負面影響。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/a8439bf4-4eb3-11e4-a1ef-00144feab7de.html#axzz3R9QPbwW5|title=Ebola poses $33bn threat to west Africa economy as human cost grows|date=08-10-2014|accessdate=2015-02-25|publisher=''[[金融時報|Financial Times]]''|archive-date=2016-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160221112606/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/a8439bf4-4eb3-11e4-a1ef-00144feab7de.html#axzz3R9QPbwW5|dead-url=no}}</ref>數以千計的利比里亞、幾內亞和塞拉利昂居民受到檢疫隔離，長時間缺乏足夠的食物，[[聯合國|聯合國]][[世界糧食計劃署|世界糧食計劃署]]採取了相應行動。<ref name="Common Dreams "/>8月16日，{{link-en|蒙羅維亞西點|West Point, Monrovia}}的檢疫隔離中心發生了骚乱。一群示威者大肆破壞以示對政府及醫護人員的不滿，他們稱此次爆發乃當局的鑿空之論。不少正受醫療監護的病人（連帶沾有鮮血的床上用品）逃脫，為疫情雪上加霜。<ref name="LiberiaQuarantine">{{cite news| title = Whole of West Point area at risk after Ebola quarantine centre attacked and looted| url = http://www.liberianews.net/index.php/sid/224841413| date = 2014-08-17| accessdate = 2015-02-25| publisher = Liberia News.Net| archive-date = 2016-03-30| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160330145249/http://www.liberianews.net/index.php/sid/224841413| dead-url = no}}</ref>

====刚果民主共和国====
{{main|2014年刚果民主共和国埃博拉病毒疫情}}
2014年8至11月期間，[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]第七度爆發伊波拉出血熱，地點為[[赤道省|赤道省]]博恩区。疫情最終在世衛及[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]等各方的致力幫助下得到控制。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.who.int/features/2014/drc-beats-ebola/en/|title=Democratic Republic of the Congo: The country that knows how to beat Ebola|publisher=World Health Organization|date=12-2014|accessdate=2015-02-26|archive-date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226005300/http://www.who.int/features/2014/drc-beats-ebola/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此次爆發與西非疫症無直接關係。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/ebola/2-september-2014/en/ | title=Virological Analysis: no link between Ebola outbreaks in west Africa and Democratic Republic of Congo | publisher=World Health Organization | date=02-09-2014 | accessdate=2015-02-27 | archive-date=2014-11-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141121121328/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/news/ebola/2-september-2014/en/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

自2018年8月疫情暴发以来，已报告超過3000例埃博拉病例，其中超過2000人死亡。到目前为止，疫情主要集中在东部的 North Kivu 和 Ituri 省，但最近它传播到了靠近[[卢旺达|卢旺达]]边境的Goma市，该市有近200万人口，属于地区交通枢纽，每天有1.5万人穿过边界从 Goma 进入卢旺达。该市还有国际航班。WHO总干事 Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus 博士2019年7月18日宣布，刚果民主共和国的埃博拉疫情为国际突发公共卫生事件。<ref>{{cite web |title=WHO 宣布埃博拉疫情为国际性危机 |url=https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=61407 |website=科技行者 |accessdate=2019-07-18 |archive-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222085711/https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=61407 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

====其他地区====
受到西非疫症的影響，其他地區亦相繼出現零星個案。[[英國|英國]]有一名護士染病，後在[[倫敦|倫敦]]{{link-en|皇家自由醫院|Royal Free Hospital}}的高危[[隔離病房|隔離病房]]接受診治，並成功康復。<ref name="WHO_UK">{{cite web |url=http://apps.who.int/ebolaweb/sitreps/20141231/20141231.pdf |title=Ebola response roadmap - Situation report - 31 December 2014 |publisher=World Health Organization |date=2014-12-31 |accessdate=2015-02-26 |archive-date=2014-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231222250/http://apps.who.int/ebolaweb/sitreps/20141231/20141231.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[美國|美國]]與[[西班牙|西班牙]]分別出現四宗（其中一人死亡）及一宗的境外移入案例，患者均為醫護人員。在嚴格的醫療監控下，病毒沒有進一步擴散。<ref name="WHO_Outside_Africa">{{cite web |url=http://apps.who.int/ebola/en/ebola-situation-report/situation-reports/ebola-situation-report-18-february-2015 |title=Ebola response roadmap - Situation report 24 December 2014 |publisher=World Health Organization |date=2015-02-18 |accessdate=2015-02-26 |archive-date=2015-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222081521/http://apps.who.int/ebola/en/ebola-situation-report/situation-reports/ebola-situation-report-18-february-2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===2018年===
{{Main|2018年剛果赤道省伊波拉出血熱爆發}}
2018年5月，刚果民主共和国西北部[[赤道省|赤道省]]比科罗镇及周边地区暴发新一轮埃博拉疫情，累计疑似病例45例，其中14例确诊，25人死亡。[[世卫组织|世卫组织]]将疫情在刚果民主共和国全国传播的风险评估等级从“高”级别提升至“非常高”，地区传播风险等级由“中等”提升至“高”<ref>[http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-05/20/c_129876052.htm 世卫组织：刚果（金）埃博拉疫情传播风险“非常高”] {{Wayback|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2018-05/20/c_129876052.htm |date=20200901174817 }}.新华网.</ref>。
{{Main|2018年－2019年剛果基伍伊波拉出血熱爆發}}
2018年爆發，截至2019年7月17日累計病例2896例、累計死亡人數1698人，目前持續發生。2019年7月17日[[世卫组织|世卫组织]]列為「国际关注的突发公共衛生事件」（Public Health Emergency of International Concern, PHEIC）

=== 2020年 ===
2020年6月1日，刚果民主共和国爆发新一轮埃博拉疫情，但總體嚴重程度低於同時期爆發的[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.who.int/news-room/detail/01-06-2020-new-ebola-outbreak-detected-in-northwest-democratic-republic-of-the-congo-who-surge-team-supporting-the-response|title=New Ebola outbreak detected in northwest Democratic Republic of the Congo; WHO surge team supporting the response|author=WHO|date=2020-06-01|work=|publisher=|accessdate=2020-06-01|language=|format=|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010190251/https://www.who.int/news-room/detail/01-06-2020-new-ebola-outbreak-detected-in-northwest-democratic-republic-of-the-congo-who-surge-team-supporting-the-response|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==社會文化議題==
===生物武器===
[[伊波拉病毒屬|伊波拉病毒屬]]的所有成員均被歸入[[生物安全防護水平|第四類生物危險品]]及[[美國疾病預防控制中心|美國疾病預防控制中心]]的甲級[[生物恐怖主義|生物恐怖主義]]範疇<ref name="Ansari2014">{{cite journal|author=Ansari AA|title=Clinical features and pathobiology of Ebolavirus infection|journal=J Autoimmun|volume=S0896-8411|issue=14|pages=00130–9|date=09-2014|pmid=25260583|doi=10.1016/j.jaut.2014.09.001}}</ref><ref name="MacNeil2012">{{cite journal|author=MacNeil A, Rollin PE|title=Ebola and Marburg hemorrhagic fevers: neglected tropical diseases?|journal=PLoS Negl Trop Dis|volume=6|issue=6|pages=e1546|date=06-2012|pmid=22761967|pmc=3385614|doi=10.1371/journal.pntd.0001546}}</ref>；此類病毒具備成為[[生物武器|生物武器]]的潛能<ref name="pmid11988060">{{cite journal | author = Borio L, Inglesby T, Peters CJ, Schmaljohn AL, Hughes JM, Jahrling PB, Ksiazek T, Johnson KM, Meyerhoff A, O'Toole T, Ascher MS, Bartlett J, Breman JG, Eitzen EM, Hamburg M, Hauer J, Henderson DA, Johnson RT, Kwik G, Layton M, Lillibridge S, Nabel GJ, Osterholm MT, Perl TM, Russell P, Tonat K | title = Hemorrhagic fever viruses as biological weapons: medical and public health management | journal = Journal of the American Medical Association | volume = 287 | issue = 18 | pages = 2391–405 | year = 2002 | pmid = 11988060 | doi = 10.1001/jama.287.18.2391 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author = Salvaggio MR, Baddley JW | title = Other viral bioweapons: Ebola and Marburg hemorrhagic fever |url = https://archive.org/details/sim_dermatologic-clinics_2004-07_22_3/page/291 | journal = Dermatologic clinics | volume = 22 | issue = 3 | pages = 291–302, vi | year = 2004 | pmid = 15207310 | doi = 10.1016/j.det.2004.03.003 }}</ref>，但因無法長久逗留於空氣中而難以成為[[大規模殺傷性武器|大規模殺傷性武器]]<ref name="Zubray">{{cite book |title=Agents of Bioterrorism: Pathogens and Their Weaponization | publisher=[[哥倫比亞大學出版社|Columbia University Press]]| author=Zubray, Geoffrey | year=2013 | location=New York, USA | pages=73–74 | isbn=9780231518130}}</ref>。不過，前蘇聯生化武器研究部副主任{{link-en|肯·阿里貝克|Ken Alibek}}相信，伊波拉能與[[天花|天花]]結合，成為一種具有大殺傷力及高傳染性的{{link-en|基因重組病毒|Recombinant virus}}。<ref name="Alibek/Tucker (interviewer)">{{cite web | url=http://cns.miis.edu/npr/pdfs/alibek63.pdf | title=Biological Weapons in the Former Soviet Union: An Interview With Dr. Kenneth Alibek | publisher=Center for Nonproliferation Studies, Monterey Institute of International Studies | work=The Nonproliferation Review/Spring-Summer 1999 | date=1999 | accessdate=2014-08-20 | author=Alibek, Kenneth, Tucker, Jonathan B. (interviewer) | pages=8 | archive-date=2015-07-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703195235/http://cns.miis.edu/npr/pdfs/alibek63.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>

===大眾文化===
過去數十年來，多部暢銷小說及電影著作均以伊波拉出血熱為題，以戲劇化或寫實的方式敘述不同年份的爆發。<ref>{{cite book | last = Preston | first = Richard | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=E6BKpf2tSkoC | title = The Hot Zone, A Terrifying True Story | year = 1995 | publisher = Anchor Books | isbn = 0-385-47956-5 | oclc = 32052009 | access-date = 2015-02-25 | archive-date = 2020-08-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200801065239/https://books.google.com/books?id=E6BKpf2tSkoC | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Close|first=William T.|author-link=|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=1IvgAAAAMAAJ|title=Ebola: A Documentary Novel of Its First Explosion|year=1995|location=New York|publisher=Ballantine Books|isbn=0804114323|oclc=32753758|access-date=2015-02-25|archive-date=2017-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119065017/https://books.google.com/books?id=1IvgAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Close|first=William T.|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=BX0gAQAAIAAJ|title=Ebola: Through the Eyes of the People|location=Marbleton, Wyoming|publisher=Meadowlark Springs Productions|year=2002|isbn=0970337116|oclc=49193962|access-date=2015-02-25|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801065836/https://books.google.com/books?id=BX0gAQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[西非伊波拉病毒疫症|西非疫症]]期間，多部以電子或印刷書籍形式對外發表的私人著作，含有誤導成分。世衛及[[聯合國|聯合國]]批評有關資訊助長了疾病的流行。<ref>{{cite news|last=Dewey|first=Caitlin|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2014/10/02/popular-on-amazon-wildly-misleading-self-published-books-about-ebola-by-random-people-without-medical-degrees/|title=Popular on Amazon: Wildly misleading self-published books about Ebola, by random people without medical degrees|date=02-10-2014|publisher=[[華盛頓郵報|''The Washington Post'']]|accessdate=2014-10-27|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001133450/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp/2014/10/02/popular-on-amazon-wildly-misleading-self-published-books-about-ebola-by-random-people-without-medical-degrees/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

深入伊波拉疫區工作的医护人員，獲美国《[[时代杂志|时代杂志]]》评为2014“年度风云人物”。<ref>{{cite news| author=| title=Ebola Fighters Are TIME's Person of the Year 2014| url=http://time.com/time-person-of-the-year-ebola-fighters-choice/| work=''Time Inc''| accessdate=2015-02-26| date=10-12-2014| archive-date=2018-02-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180227175205/http://time.com/time-person-of-the-year-ebola-fighters-choice/| dead-url=no}}</ref>

==其他動物==
科學家自本世紀初起，密切監察着其他動物的疫情，希望能盡量預防人類感染個案。<ref name="Cite pmid|15752448">{{cite journal | author = Rouquet P, Froment JM, Bermejo M, Kilbourn A, Karesh W, Reed P, Kumulungui B, Yaba P, Délicat A, Rollin PE, Leroy EM | title = Wild animal mortality monitoring and human Ebola outbreaks, Gabon and Republic of Congo, 2001–2003 | journal = Emerging Infectious Diseases | volume = 11 | issue = 2 | pages = 283–290 | date = Feb 2005 | pmid = 15752448 | pmc = 3320460 | doi = 10.3201/eid1102.040533 | url = http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/article/11/2/pdfs/04-0533.pdf | issn = 1080-6040 | format = Free full text | accessdate = 2015-02-26 | archive-date = 2020-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201222085730/https://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/article/11/2/pdfs/04-0533.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>
===靈長類動物===
伊波拉病毒對其他[[靈長動物|靈長動物]]同樣致命。<ref name="pmid23813435">{{cite journal | author = Choi JH, Croyle MA | title = Emerging targets and novel approaches to Ebola virus prophylaxis and treatment | journal = BioDrugs | volume = 27 | issue = 6 | pages = 565–83 | year = 2013 | pmid = 23813435 | doi = 10.1007/s40259-013-0046-1 }}</ref>2002至2003年间，在一个名為“{{lang|en|Lossi}}”的保育區，伊波拉疫症使每420平方公里的[[黑猩猩|黑猩猩]]跟踪率下降了88%。<ref name="doi10.1126/science.1092528">{{cite journal | author = Leroy EM, Rouquet P, Formenty P, Souquière S, Kilbourne A, Froment JM, Bermejo M, Smit S, Karesh W, Swanepoel R, Zaki SR, Rollin PE | title = Multiple Ebola virus transmission events and rapid decline of central African wildlife | journal = Science | volume = 303 | issue = 5656 | pages = 387–390 | year = 2004 | pmid = 14726594 | doi = 10.1126/science.1092528 | bibcode = 2004Sci...303..387L }}</ref>這些動物染病的主因是進食了受污染的肉類，而非為相互觸摸或觸碰到屍體。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Formenty P, Boesch C, Wyers M, Steiner C, Donati F, Dind F, Walker F, Le Guenno B | title = Ebola virus outbreak among wild chimpanzees living in a rain forest of Côte d'Ivoire | journal = The Journal of infectious diseases | volume = Suppl 1 | issue = s1 | pages = S120–S126 | year = 1999 | pmid = 9988175 | doi = 10.1086/514296 | series = 179 }}</ref>雷斯頓病毒於初次亮相時，奪取了不少實驗室猴子的性命。1989年末，隸屬黑澤爾頓科研產品公司（{{lang|en|Hazelton Research Products}}）的[[里斯顿|雷斯頓]]檢疫區中，一群由[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]運來的[[食蟹獼猴|食蟹獼猴]]罹患神秘致命疾病，並被誤診為感染{{link-en|猴出血熱病毒|Simian hemorrhagic fever virus}}。動物病理學家後將活組織樣本，寄給了位於[[馬里蘭|馬里蘭]][[迪特里克堡|迪特里克堡]]的[[美國陸軍傳染病醫學研究院|美國陸軍傳染病醫學研究院]]。[[酶聯免疫吸附試驗|酶聯免疫吸附試驗]]的結果證實了此樣本含有針對伊波拉病毒的[[抗體|抗體]]<ref name="Preston">{{cite book |title=The Hot Zone |url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780385427104 | publisher=Random House | author=Preston, Richard | year=1994 | location=New York | pages=[https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780385427104/page/300 300] | isbn=978-0679437840}}</ref>，結果與[[電子顯微鏡|電子顯微鏡]]映像相乎<ref name="McCormick 1999 277–279">{{harvnb|McCormick|Fisher-Hoch|1999|pp=277–279}}</ref>。尚未因病致死的猴子被[[安樂死|人道毀滅]]，屍體交由德特里克堡的病理及病毒學家研究，最終被安全棄置。<ref name="Preston" />178名曾接觸這些猴子的工作人員中，有6位出現血清轉換的現象（即其[[血清|血清]]被檢測到[[抗體|抗體]]，卻並無出現任何症狀）。<ref name="Waterman 1999">{{Cite book|last=Waterman|first=Tara|url=http://www.stanford.edu/group/virus/filo/ebor.html|title=Ebola Reston Outbreaks|accessdate=2015-02-26|year=1999|publisher=[[史丹福大學出版社|''Stanford University Press'']]|archive-date=2008-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080616192533/http://www.stanford.edu/group/virus/filo/ebor.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="isbn0-7910-8505-8"/>最後，研究人員獨立出一種出現於[[亞洲|亞洲]]、名為“雷斯頓病毒”的新型伊波拉病毒種。<ref name="Preston" />[[美國疾病預防控制中心|美國疾病預防控制中心]]總結，雷斯頓種雖與其他伊波拉病毒共被歸入第四類生物危險品，但它對人類的致病性不高。<ref name="McCormick 1999 298–299">{{harvnb|McCormick|Fisher-Hoch|1999|pp=298–300}}</ref>

===其他類別===
伊波拉病毒也出現於其他種類的動物身上。雷斯頓病毒曾感染了[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]、[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]及[[意大利|意大利]]的豬隻。<ref name="Weingartl_2013">{{cite journal | author = Weingartl HM, Nfon C, Kobinger G | title = Review of Ebola virus infections in domestic animals | journal = Dev Biol (Basel) | volume = 135 | issue = | pages = 211–8 | year = 2013 | pmid = 23689899 | doi = 10.1159/000178495 }}</ref>雖然一項於2012年進行的實驗證實了這類病毒能在沒有接觸的情況下，從豬擴散至其他靈長動物身上，但該測試無法證明病毒能以同樣的方式，於靈長動物間傳播。<ref name="Weingartl2012">{{cite journal | author = Weingartl HM, Embury-Hyatt C, Nfon C, Leung A, Smith G, Kobinger G | title = Transmission of Ebola virus from pigs to non-human primates | journal = Sci Rep | volume = 2 | issue = | pages = 811 |date=November 2012 | pmid = 23155478 | pmc = 3498927 | doi = 10.1038/srep00811 }}</ref> 在非洲，狗隻經常進食或含有伊波拉病毒的[[食腐動物|腐肉]]，但甚少出現[[醫學徵象|病癥]]。一項2005年的測試顯示，出現在伊波拉爆發地的狗對模式種病毒的{{link-en|血清陽性率|Seroprevalence}}為30%，但處於較遠地區的則為9%。<ref name="pmid15757552">{{cite journal |author = Allela L, Boury O, Pouillot R, Délicat A, Yaba P, Kumulungui B, Rouquet P, Gonzalez JP, Leroy EM | title = Ebola virus antibody prevalence in dogs and human risk | journal = Emerging Infect. Dis. | volume = 11 | issue = 3 | pages = 385–90 | year = 2005 | pmid = 15757552 | pmc = 3298261 | doi = 10.3201/eid1103.040981 }}</ref>另外，[[羚羊|羚羊]]也是主要的帶病動物。<ref name="Peterson AT, Bauer JT, Mills JN 2004 40–47"/>

[[世衛|世衛]]建議使用[[次氯酸鈉|次氯酸鈉]]（即漂白水）或其他適當的[[清潔劑|清潔劑]]定期消毒農場，並隔離任何疑似感染個案，以防病毒傳染至其他動物群體。<ref name=WHO_Fact_Sheet/>

