===治療方案===
目前尚未有安全、可供廣泛使用的伊波拉出血熱治療藥物或預防疫苗，各个方向的科研項目仍在进行之中。
====藥物治療====
多種藥物均具備治療伊波拉出血熱的潛質，當中以抗病毒及抗體藥物為主流的研究對象。獲日本官方批准存貨的[[法匹拉韋|法匹拉韋]]在老鼠身上取得理想成效。<ref name="Gatherer 2014" /><ref name="pmid24583123">{{cite journal|last1=Oestereich|first1=L|last2=Lüdtke|first2=A|last3=Wurr|first3=S|last4=Rieger|first4=T|last5=Muñoz-Fontela|first5=C|last6=Günther|first6=S|title=Successful treatment of advanced Ebola virus infection with T-705 (favipiravir) in a small animal model.|journal=Antiviral research|date=2014 May|volume=105|pages=17-21|pmid=24583123}}</ref>美國 {{lang|en|BioCryst}} 藥廠研發的廣譜分子“{{lang|en|BCX4430}}”及“{{lang|en|Brincidofovir}}”亦為候選者之一：前者獲[[美國陸軍傳染病醫學研究所|美國陸軍傳染病醫學研究所]]承認其[[動物測試|動物測試]]結果<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/davidkroll/2014/08/29/biocryst-to-launch-nhp-ebola-drug-safety-studies-within-weeks/|title=BioCryst to Launch NHP Ebola Drug Safety, Efficacy Studies 'Within Weeks'|author=David Kroll|date=2014-08-29|work=''[[福布斯|Forbes]]''|accessdate=2015-02-27|archive-date=2020-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222085725/https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidkroll/2014/08/29/biocryst-to-launch-nhp-ebola-drug-safety-studies-within-weeks/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而後者則獲美國食物安全中心批准進入臨床試驗程序<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/35b73c5ff32b472dac9de0df38898fb0/chimerix-gets-fda-ok-test-drug-ebola|title=Chimerix gets FDA approval to test drug for Ebola.|newspaper=Associated Press|author=|date=2014-10-17|accessdate=2014-10-31|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023153535/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/35b73c5ff32b472dac9de0df38898fb0/chimerix-gets-fda-ok-test-drug-ebola|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名利比里亞醫生在2014年9月，以原本用於抑制[[HIV|愛滋病病毒]]的藥物[[拉米夫定|拉米夫定]]輔以[[抗生素|抗生素]]（針對[[機會性感染|機會性細菌感染]]）及[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]，治愈了15名伊波拉病人中的13人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/09/27/health/ebola-hiv-drug/|title=Doctor treats Ebola with HIV drug in Liberia – seemingly successfully|author=Elizabeth Cohen|publisher=CNN News|date=2014-09-27|work=CNN|accessdate=2015-02-27|archive-date=2014-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140930105526/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/09/27/health/ebola-hiv-drug|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於不肯定因素過多及樣本量太少，病毒學家對此療法表示懷疑；[[國立衛生研究院_(美國)|美國國立衛生研究院]]亦未能於初步體外試驗中證實其功效，但表示會繼續研究。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/to-your-health/wp/2014/10/02/a-liberian-doctor-is-using-hiv-drugs-to-treat-ebola-victims-the-nih-is-intrigued/|title=A Liberian doctor is using HIV drugs to treat Ebola victims. The NIH is intrigued|author=Elahe Izadi|publisher=Washington Post|date=02-10-2014|work=''Washington Post''|accessdate=2015-02-27|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001135818/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/to-your-health/wp/2014/10/02/a-liberian-doctor-is-using-hiv-drugs-to-treat-ebola-victims-the-nih-is-intrigued/|dead-url=no}}</ref>由中國四環醫藥公司及軍事醫學院研製了“{{lang|en|JK-05}}”，宣稱通過動物測試且進入臨床試驗階段。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1582834/ebola-virus-approved-mainland-emergency-use-only|title=Ebola virus drug approved on mainland for emergency use only|author=Zhuang Pinghui|publisher=[[南華早報|''South China Morning Post'']]|date=01-09-2014|accessdate=2015-02-27|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816132342/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1582834/ebola-virus-approved-mainland-emergency-use-only|dead-url=no}}</ref>除此，研究者一叩洪鐘，向其他種類的抗病毒物質著手。<ref name="pmid11888653">{{cite journal | author = Bray M, Paragas J | title = Experimental therapy of filovirus infections | journal = Antiviral Res. | volume = 54 | issue = 1 | pages = 1–17 | year = 2002 | pmid = 11888653 | doi = 10.1016/S0166-3542(02)00005-0 }}</ref><ref name="pmid12615303">{{cite journal | author = Bray M | title = Defense against filoviruses used as biological weapons | journal = Antiviral Res. | volume = 57 | issue = 1-2 | pages = 53–60 | year = 2003 | pmid = 12615303 | doi = 10.1016/S0166-3542(02)00200-0 }}</ref>一些天然化合物（如：“{{lang|en|Scytovirin}}”及“{{lang|en|Griffithsin}}”）<ref>{{cite journal | author = Garrison AR, Giomarelli BG, Lear-Rooney CM, Saucedo CJ, Yellayi S, Krumpe LR, Rose M, Paragas J, Bray M, Olinger GG, McMahon JB, Huggins J, O'Keefe BR | title = The cyanobacterial lectin scytovirin displays potent in vitro and in vivo activity against Zaire Ebola virus | journal = Antiviral Research | year = 2014 | pmid = 25265598 | doi = 10.1016/j.antiviral.2014.09.012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Barton C, Kouokam JC, Lasnik AB, Foreman O, Cambon A, Brock G, Montefiori DC, Vojdani F, McCormick AA, O'Keefe BR, Palmer KE | title = Activity of and effect of subcutaneous treatment with the broad-spectrum antiviral lectin griffithsin in two laboratory rodent models | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_antimicrobial-agents-and-chemotherapy_2014-01_58_1/page/120 | journal = Antimicrobial Agents and Chemotherapy | volume = 58 | issue = 1 | pages = 120–7 | year = 2014 | pmid = 24145548 | pmc = 3910741 | doi = 10.1128/AAC.01407-13 }}</ref>、合成藥（“{{lang|en|DZNep}}”、“{{lang|en|FGI-103}}”、“{{lang|en|FGI-104}}”、“{{lang|en|FGI-106}}”、“{{lang|en|dUY11}}”與“{{lang|en|LJ-001}}”）<ref name="pmid9988190">{{cite journal |author = Huggins J, Zhang ZX, Bray M | title = Antiviral drug therapy of filovirus infections: S-adenosylhomocysteine hydrolase inhibitors inhibit Ebola virus in vitro and in a lethal mouse model | journal = J. Infect. Dis. | volume = 179 Suppl 1 | issue = | pages = S240–7 | year = 1999 | pmid = 9988190 | doi = 10.1086/514316 }}</ref>、不同組合性生化物質均包括在內<ref>'''1.''' {{cite journal |author = De Clercq E | title = A Cutting-Edge View on the Current State of Antiviral Drug Development | journal = Medicinal Research Reviews | pages = n/a | year = 2013 | pmid = 23495004 | doi = 10.1002/med.21281 }}<br />'''2.''' {{cite journal|title=Inhibition of Lassa virus and Ebola virus infection in host cells treated with the kinase inhibitors genistein and tyrphostin|journal=Archives of Virology|doi=10.1007/s00705-011-1115-8|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s0