ue = 13 | pages = 7754–7 | year = 2013 | pmid = 23616649 | pmc = 3700280 | doi = 10.1128/JVI.00173-13 }}<br />'''6.''' {{cite journal | author = Elshabrawy HA, Fan J, Haddad CS, Ratia K, Broder CC, Caffrey M, Prabhakar BS | title = Identification of a broad-spectrum antiviral small molecule against severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus and Ebola, Hendra, and Nipah viruses by using a novel high-throughput screening assay | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-virology_2014-04_88_8/page/4353 | journal = Journal of Virology | volume = 88 | issue = 8 | pages = 4353–65 | year = 2014 | pmid = 24501399 | pmc = 3993759 | doi = 10.1128/JVI.03050-13 }}<br />'''7.''' {{cite journal |author = Mudhasani R, Kota KP, Retterer C, Tran JP, Whitehouse CA, Bavari S | title = High content image-based screening of a protease inhibitor library reveals compounds broadly active against Rift Valley fever virus and other highly pathogenic RNA viruses | journal = PLoS Neglected Tropical Diseases | volume = 8 | issue = 8 | pages = e3095 | year = 2014 | pmid = 25144302 | pmc = 4140764 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pntd.0003095 }}<br />'''8.''' {{cite journal |author = Johnson JC, Martinez O, Honko AN, Hensley LE, Olinger GG, Basler CF | title = Pyridinyl imidazole inhibitors of p38 MAP kinase impair viral entry and reduce cytokine induction by Zaire ebolavirus in human dendritic cells | journal = Antiviral Research | volume = 107 | pages = 102–9 | year = 2014 | pmid = 24815087 | pmc = 4103912 | doi = 10.1016/j.antiviral.2014.04.014 }}</ref>。名為“{{lang|en|[[ZMapp|ZMapp]]}}”的實驗性、含三種單克隆[[抗體|抗體]]的藥物於獼猴身上取得成效。<ref name=NYTseconddrug/><ref>{{cite news |author=Nathan Seppa |title=ZMapp drug fully protects monkeys against Ebola virus |url=https://www.sciencenews.org/article/zmapp-drug-fully-protects-monkeys-against-ebola-virus |work=Science News |publisher=Society for Science & the Public |date=2014-08-29 |accessdate=2015-02-27 |archive-date=2019-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513091115/https://www.sciencenews.org/article/zmapp-drug-fully-protects-monkeys-against-ebola-virus |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[美國衛生及公共服務部|美國衛生及公共服務部]]促請多個研究中心加快生產，以備不時之需。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/seattle/blog/health-care-inc/2014/10/amgen-works-with-gates-foundation-to-ramp-up-ebola.html|title=Amgen works with Gates Foundation to ramp up Ebola drug ZMapp production|date=2014-10-20|accessdate=2015-02-27|publisher=American City Business Journals|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816134526/https://www.bizjournals.com/seattle/blog/health-care-inc/2014/10/amgen-works-with-gates-foundation-to-ramp-up-ebola.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>有[[泰國|泰國]]研究團隊宣佈成功以病毒合成片段製成了一種抗體藥物。世衛及美國國立衛生研究院已經安排測試，惟此藥物仍有待改進。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.voanews.com/content/thai-researchers-claim-breakthrough-in-ebola-treatment/2471222.html|title=Thai researchers claim breakthrough in Ebola treatment|author=Ron Corben|publisher=Voice of America News|date=03-10-2014|accessdate=2015-02-27|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310121310/http://www.voanews.com/content/thai-researchers-claim-breakthrough-in-ebola-treatment/2471222.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>原用以治療不育及[[乳癌|乳癌]]的{{link-en|克羅米芬|clomiphene}}及{{link-en|托瑞米芬|Toremifene}}亦見有效<ref name="Johansen_2013">{{cite journal | author = Johansen LM, Brannan JM, Delos SE, Shoemaker CJ, Stossel A, Lear C, Hoffstrom BG, Dewald LE, Schornberg KL, Scully C, Lehár J, Hensley LE, White JM, Olinger GG | title = FDA-approved selective estrogen receptor modulators inhibit Ebola virus infection | journal = Sci Transl Med | volume = 5 | issue = 190 | pages = 190ra79 | year = 2013 | pmid = 23785035 | pmc = 3955358 | doi = 10.1126/scitranslmed.3005471 | laysummary = http://www.healthline.com/health-news/tech-breast-cancer-drugs-fight-ebola-virus-infection-062013 | laysource = Healthline Networks, Inc. | access-date = 2014-07-29 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031447/http://www.healthline.com/health-news/tech-breast-cancer-drugs-fight-ebola-virus-infection-062013 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，它們分別治愈了90%及50%的實驗白鼠<ref name="Johansen_2013"/>。2014年的一項體外測試發現，用以治療心律失常的粒子通道阻滯藥[[胺碘酮|胺碘酮]]能阻止伊波拉病毒進入細胞。<ref name="pmid24710028">{{cite journal | author = Gehring G, Rohrmann K, Atenchong N, Mittler E, Becker S, Dahlmann F, Pöhlmann S, Vondran FW, David S, Manns MP, Ciesek S, von Hahn T | title = The clinically approved drugs amiodarone, dronedarone and verapamil inhibit filovirus cell entry | journal = J. Antimicrob. Chemother. | volume = 69 | issue = 8 | pages = 2123–31 | year = 2014 | pmid = 24710028 | doi = 10.1093/jac/dku091 }}</ref>

