nary-didn-t-get-tkm-ebola-drug-tekmira-says-1.2726740|dead-url=no}}</ref>由美國研發的{{link-en|薩雷普塔治療|Sarepta Therapeutics}}則已經通過第一期临床试验的階段。<ref name="pmid25155593">{{cite journal | author = Heald AE, Iversen PL, Saoud JB, Sazani P, Charleston JS, Axtelle T, Wong M, Smith WB, Vutikullird A, Kaye E | title = Safety and pharmacokinetic profiles of phosphorodiamidate morpholino oligomers with activity against Ebola virus and Marburg virus: results of two single ascending dose studies | journal = Antimicrobial Agents and Chemotherapy | date = 2014-08-25 | pmid = 25155593 | doi = 10.1128/AAC.03442-14 | url = http://aac.asm.org/content/early/2014/08/19/AAC.03442-14.full.pdf+html | volume = 58 | issue = 11 | pages = 6639–47 | access-date = 2014-11-03 | archive-date = 2018-08-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180804192957/http://aac.asm.org/content/early/2014/08/19/AAC.03442-14.full.pdf+html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

